## 🔌 WIRING DIAGRAM

```
ESP32          L298N Motor Driver
─────          ─────────────────
GPIO 27  ───► IN1   (Left Motor Forward)
GPIO 26  ───► IN2   (Left Motor Backward)
GPIO 25  ───► IN3   (Right Motor Forward)
GPIO 33  ───► IN4   (Right Motor Backward)
GPIO 14  ───► ENA   (Left Motor Speed PWM)
GPIO 12  ───► ENB   (Right Motor Speed PWM)
GND      ───► GND
           OUT1/OUT2 ───► Left Motor
           OUT3/OUT4 ───► Right Motor
           12V ───► 9V Battery+

ESP32          HC-SR04 FRONT
─────          ─────────────
GPIO  5  ───► TRIG
GPIO 18  ◄─── ECHO
3.3V     ───► VCC
GND      ───► GND

ESP32          HC-SR04 REAR
─────          ────────────
GPIO 19  ───► TRIG
GPIO 21  ◄─── ECHO
3.3V     ───► VCC
GND      ───► GND

ESP32          LEDs + BUZZER
─────          ─────────────
GPIO 32  ───► [220Ω] ───► Green LED ───► GND
GPIO 35  ───► [220Ω] ───► Red LED   ───► GND
GPIO 34  ───► [220Ω] ───► Yellow LED───► GND
GPIO 13  ───► Buzzer (+) ───► GND
```

